import React from 'react'
import Login from './Login'
import Home from './Home'
import {Redirect, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/" component={Home}/>
            <Route exact path="/login" component={Login}/>
            <Redirect to="/" />
            </Switch>   
        </>
    )
}

export default App
